Text: FW Houston Visit Dear Mr I enjoyed meeting you at the recent World Economic Forum in Washington DC I will be in Houston next week and would like to meet with you to discuss your groups activities and Bermudas goal as a Telecommunications hub and Ecommerce jurisdiction If you have sometime available between Tuesday and Thursday of next week kindly let me know Sincerely yours Renee Webb Minister of Telecommunicationa and Ecommerce Government of Bermuda
